First fact(sav thi pela aano video bnai ne upload ker kale sanje sudhi ma)
Why do india buy 85% Crude oil form asian/midel easten countrys and only 1% of 
from Russia infact of our good relation?

Ans:- Crudel oil ka price(60$ dollar/barrel) same hai agar india khahi se be buy kare,
      per crude oil sirf 2 tarike se transport ho shakta hai 1. pipeke zariye ya to
      2. ship ke zariye, india or russia ke bich koi be pipeline jesa kuch nai hai
      or naki aane wale kuch samye me bane ga or ship ke zariye russia se oil transport
      kerna costly padega isiliye wo east asian/middel country se buy kerte hai taki 
      transportation cost kam rahe.
      
Second Fact
How dose the Air-Bag opens in the car?

Ans:- Car ke Stearing wheel or tires me speed sencers hote hai,
      ye sencers presure sencers se connected hote hai jo ki ek heating
      coil se connected hota hai,heating coil ke aage hirdogen gas hoti
      hai, accedent ke samai presure sencer heating coil ko activate
      kerte hai jo turant hi gas koo garam kerk airbag ko inflate deta hai
      jise accident me death or badi injuries ke chances come ker deta hai.

Third Fact
Why do indian goverment and the whole world are protecting Tigers?

Ans:- 100 sal pehle puri duniya me 1,00,000 se b zyada tigers the or abhi
      sirf 4,000 or usme sebhi 3,000 to sirf india me hai, jese aapko pata
      ki tigers forest food chain me top pe aate hai or tiger wo animals ko
      khate hai joo pedh or podhe khate hai agar tiger ki species vilupt ho
      gai to un animals ki death rate kum ho jaye gi jise future me wo tree
      eating animals bhed jaye ge or 50% of forest ko khaker khatum ker denge
      jise globel warming bhed jaye gi jo nature ko harm are gi,... i think
      iske jaise gorvement ko or ideas aane chaiye jise glober warming kum hoo
